snippet.title: Paramount Entertainment UK
snippet.description: Welcome to the official Paramount Entertainment UK YouTube channel! Browse our videos for the latest Paramount Pictures home entertainment releases and watch your favorite films such as Sonic the Hedgehog, A Quiet Place and classics like Top Gun, Transformers, Star Trek, Forrest Gump, Mission: Impossible, Pulp Fiction, Kill Bill and many more. Be sure to subscribe to get a first look at exciting footage.
